Definition: some abrupt occurrence that interrupts an ongoing activity
Example: the telephone is an annoying interruption; there was a break in the action when a player was hurt
Synonyms: break, verb, stative, happening, some, abrupt, occurrence, that, interrupts, an, ongoing, activity, the, telephone, is, annoying, there, was, a, in, action, when, player, hurt
Category: noun.event
